Name: spindle epithelial tumor with thymus-like differentiation tumor
Definition: A thyroid gland carcinoma that has_material_basis_in compact bundles of long spindle epithelial cells that merge with tubulopapillary structures and/or mucinous glands.

Name: thyroid gland anaplastic carcinoma
Definition: A thyroid gland carcinoma that is composed of undifferentiated cells.

Name: thyroid gland adenocarcinoma
Definition: A thyroid gland carcinoma that derives_from epithelial cells of glandular origin.

Name: thyroid gland medullary carcinoma
Definition: A thyroid gland carcinoma that has_material_basis_in parafollicular cells.

Name: obsolete medullary carcinoma
Definition: A thyroid gland carcinoma that has_material_basis_in parafollicular cells.

Name: thyroid gland mucoepidermoid carcinoma
Definition: A thyroid gland carcinoma that is composed of groups of squamoid and mucous cells
